name: Ball Till You Fall #001
description:
“Ball Till You Fall” is a series celebrating hoop culture with material explorations through customized basketballs. 

The first 6 primary collectors will receive a limited edition 12"x 12" print: https://hypernormal.space/products/ball-till-you-fall-1-nft-and-print-bundle

Please DM directly on Twitter with your physical address after you've purchased the NFT to receive the framed print.
